{"chatKey": "chat-refund-01", "mainKey": "chat-refund-01", "threadKey": "chat-refund-01", "channelId": "channel-synthetic-demo", "chatType": "userChat", "chatId": "chat-refund-01", "language": "ko", "state": "sent", "_meta": {"provenance": "SYNTHETIC"}, "id": "msg-01-customer", "personType": "user", "personId": "user-refund-01", "plainText": "오늘 주문한 20260718-000001을 취소하면 환불이 언제 들어오나요? 급합니다.", "createdAt": 1784330400000, "updatedAt": 1784330400000}
{"chatKey": "chat-refund-01", "mainKey": "chat-refund-01", "threadKey": "chat-refund-01", "channelId": "channel-synthetic-demo", "chatType": "userChat", "chatId": "chat-refund-01", "language": "ko", "state": "sent", "_meta": {"provenance": "SYNTHETIC"}, "id": "msg-01-manager", "personType": "manager", "personId": "manager-cx-01", "plainText": "배송 전 취소가 확인되면 환불은 승인일로부터 3영업일 안에 처리됩니다.", "createdAt": 1784330445000, "updatedAt": 1784330445000}
